short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get the urls of all the current open tabs in a list

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Manage the links of your open tabs across your browser windows.

Features:
- List current window or all windows.
- Allow copying individual urls by clicking the site icon.
- Batch copy all links.
- Batch download all links to a file.
- Filter links using the search box (simple filter and regex).
- Individual links removal.
- Dark theme support.

Source Code:
https://github.com/DanSM-5/tabs-to-links
